    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 10th level, you learn to harness your presence on the battlefield to inspire greatness from others. As a bonus action, you unleash a battle cry that sways the outcome of conflict. Up to twice your Charisma modifier (minimum of 2) other creatures of your choice within 60 feet of you that can hear you double their proficiency bonus until the start of your next turn.</p><p>Additionally, the creatures you chose can make attacks of opportunity against creatures that you move using your Tempered Hand.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a long rest.</p>",
